# Folder Structure

Enforce the following folder structure for Cloudflare Workers MVC architecture:
server/                  # Root of the Cloudflare Workers project
  .gitignore             # Git ignore file
  assets/              # Static assets served by Workers
    css/               # Compiled Tailwind CSS
      *.css
    fonts/             # Web fonts
      *.woff2
      *.woff
      *.ttf
      *.css
    img/               # Images
      favicons/        # Favicon assets
        *.ico
        *.png
        *.svg
        *.webp
        *.jpg
        *.jpeg
        *.gif
      *.png
      *.svg
      *.ico
      *.webp
      *.jpg
      *.jpeg
      *.gif
    js/                # Client-side JS (HTMX, etc.)
      *.js
  migrations/            # D1 database migrations
    *.sql
  src/                   # Source code for Cloudflare Workers
    controllers/         # MVC Controllers (API & UI logic) - TypeScript
      *.ts
    models/              # MVC Models (Data layer) - TypeScript
      *.ts
    routes/              # Route definitions and handlers - TypeScript
      *.ts
    types/               # Global TypeScript type definitions
      *.ts
    utils/               # Utility functions, helpers, middleware - TypeScript
      *.ts
    views/               # Pug templates for server-side rendering
      layouts/           # Layout templates
        *.pug
      pages/             # Main page templates
        *.pug
      partials/          # Reusable Pug components
        *.pug
    server.ts            # Main entry point for the Worker (TypeScript)
  test/                  # Test files
    *.spec.ts
    *.test.ts
    env.d.ts
    tsconfig.json          # TypeScript configuration
  package.json           # Node.js project manifest
  postcss.config.js      # PostCSS config for Tailwind
  tailwind.config.js     # Tailwind CSS config
  tsconfig.json          # TypeScript configuration
  vitest.config.mts      # Vitest configuration
  wrangler.jsonc         # Wrangler configuration file
  worker-configuration.d.ts # Cloudflare Workers type definitions
